          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1360.-step-2.new1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook your coppa ham</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat.</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>coppa ham</strong> and cook for 1 minute on each side or until almost crisp. </p>\n<p>Once crisp, transfer the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>coppa</strong> to a baking tray and put it in the oven for 5 minutes. </p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1360.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1360.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1360.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
